Package: multiverse
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2020-06-21
Title: Explorable Multiverse Data Analysis and Reports in R
Description: Create Explorable Multiverse Analysis in R. Multiverse analysis is a philosophy of statistical reporting where paper authors report the outcomes of many different statistical analyses in order to show how fragile or robust their findings are.
